ji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"56b687f53e5319acf799a2fa75bd58b07a484301","tid":1234554,"uid":258927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T03:25:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/589475668207599620/590002155272798218/unknown.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.discordapp.com%2Fattachments%2F589475668207599620%2F590002155272798218%2Funknown.png&h=bd1de80c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n林鄭又再呃9me, 今次恰我唔識字!<br />\n聲明原來有2面, 中英文唔同意思!<br />\n<br />\n中文睇落好順眼, 英文攞你命三千!<br />\nSuspend咪等於暫援, 幾時恢復佢話事!<br />\n係咁依講句sorry, 佢當我地係白痴!<br />\n好多人都中伏了, 快啲傳開話佢知!<br />\n<br />\n學生無罪應釋放, 撤回惡法要堅持!<br />\n黑警背後偷偷笑, 唔當我地一回事!<br />\n幫手推上新聞紙, 快啲share俾人知!<br />\n<br />\n# 生於亂世 有種責任<br />\n# 唔可以俾佢呃9我地200萬人<br />\n<br />\n巴打絲打幫手share出呀, fb/ig/tg乜都好, 佢玩9我地200萬人太無恥!"},{"pid":"0bf13384b07ba22a9b3a58dd4d796a33efadbaad","tid":1234554,"uid":205733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e9a5d441536b30e58733a323a0984d91040b1ccd","tid":1234554,"uid":2429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c2ae31fe1d59cda23ea68e741c2941f8ba0e6623","tid":1234554,"uid":205733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dad6cf248eeb1acd6d060cc6d81113673b6b1ca2","tid":1234554,"uid":2429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T03:13:06.000Z","msg":"兩個月後仲有撚人同你衝咩，成撚日議席議席，屌你老母政黨狗。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T03:20:06.000Z","msg":"宜家警察拉9曬D人，死得仲快<br />\n你想唔想承認都好<br />\n逃犯條例要消失，得兩個方法<br />\n1.撤回<br />\n2.否決<br />\n如果政府唔會撤回呢，咪變消耗戰<br />\n你屌我老母有用咩？你有計逼到政府立刻撤回咩？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T03:23:14.000Z","msg":"我真係唔撚明點解依家二百萬人都唔撚迫佢回應，要等佢兩個月後再推先做野，咩撚野邏輯黎？當啲人係自己隻卒一叫就到？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T03:30:18.000Z","msg":"宜家有無反應先？做到梗係好，我都想<br />\n現實係政府行咗半步，唔會再理我地<br />\n仲想搶道德高地<br />\n唔忍得，無動員力，無記性一定收皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c42fb948968a07b12fdf10d7c58038d56c95b09","tid":1234554,"uid":205733,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T03:40:59.000Z","msg":"&ldquo;尋晚發夢夢到:<br />\n流動戰術既恐怖在於幾千，甚至萬人有可能突如其來佔領<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n呢班人好大威脅，因為佢地識玩輿論，知道咩時候進咩時候退，前有立法會議員，後有聖詩團/鍵盤戰士，又淨係針對林鄭老母令到佢d盟友懶得幫拖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢地增加左政府管治成本就散，無衝擊無流血，無阻到市民，無位比人入<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果警察暴力清場，就要冒住再有百萬人上街，同埋比國際社會制裁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n呢班流動民眾每次都係林鄭主動出黎挑釁市民先比壓力政府，所以出師有名<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢地行動力強，有可能一呼百應進行不合作運動，但冇咁做因為佢地係守法市民<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢地勇武但唔盲衝，有策略但冇大台，有目標亦都有耐性<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n報夢人仲話政府一日唔撤回惡法，就會成為習主席G20見Trump前既心腹大患<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n分享隔離post, 長期流動戰術+不合作運動"},{"pid":"ba3ca6b3557701a443d7bcc8058683fdcf9f363a","tid":1234554,"uid":205733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T04:05:17.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1331fc06c3245b8ea079a3ba6d3bfc5b3f96bafd","tid":1234554,"uid":137569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T04:06:07.000Z","msg":"咪講選舉可以嗎"},{"pid":"50993892fbea8fa4c43e0b3fe58205e9b5dc39a0","tid":1234554,"uid":205733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1331fc06c3245b8ea079a3ba6d3bfc5b3f96bafd","tid":1234554,"uid":137569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T04:06:07.000Z","msg":"咪講選舉可以嗎"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T04:18:04.000Z","msg":"現實問題，我都好想三兩下就撤回<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/s